msgid "Brāhmaṇakulā cepi, brāhmaṇa …"
msgstr "brahmins,"

msgctxt "mn96:16.14"
msgid "vessakulā cepi, brāhmaṇa …"
msgstr "merchants,"

msgctxt "mn96:16.15"
msgid ""
"suddakulā cepi, brāhmaṇa, agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti, so ca "
"tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ āgamma pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, "
"adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, abrahmacariyā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā "
"paṭivirato hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, pharusāya vācāya "
"paṭivirato hoti, samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti, anabhijjhālu hoti, "
"abyāpannacitto hoti, sammādiṭṭhi hoti, ārādhako hoti ñāyaṃ dhammaṃ "
"kusalan”ti."
msgstr ""
"or workers goes forth from the lay life to homelessness. Relying on the "
"teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One they refrain from "
"killing living creatures, stealing, and sex. They refrain from using speech "
"that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. And they’re not covetous or "
"malicious, and they have right view. They succeed in the procedure of the "
"skillful teaching.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn96:17.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, esukārī brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Esukārī said to him:"

msgctxt "mn96:17.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "mn96:17.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn96:17.4"
msgid "Esukārīsuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
